"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/1molhXVL/Logo_377__msi___jpg.jpg" data-lazyload-id="m1107" data-lazyload-class="module image" data-lazyload-alt="Logo" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=,hovertransition="> <img id="m1107" class="module image" src="/uploads/1molhXVL/Logo_377__msi___jpg.jpg" alt="Logo" width="202" height="202" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </a> </div> <div id="m1158" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> <div class="col hidden-sm col-sm-6 col-lg-8 col-md-6 flexCol"><div id="m1691" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m4460" class="module text smallModule"><p class="custom2" style="text-align: center;">Professional Tree Surgeons</p></div> <div id="m2132" class="module text"><p class="lightbodytext" style="text-align: center;">Serving Woking, Surrey, and the Surrounding Areas</p></div> </div> <div id="m4402" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> <div class="col col-md-3 col-lg-2 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div id="m3360" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <a href="/"  title="" aria-label="" class="imageModuleWrap" id="w_m2568" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="NPTC" data-author="" width="" height="" fetchpriority="high"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/zUrWvg9V/nptclogo1.webp" data-lazyload-id="m2568" data-lazyload-class="module image" data-lazyload-alt="NPTC" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=,hovertransition="> <img id="m2568" class="module image" src="/uploads/zUrWvg9V/nptclogo1.webp" alt="NPTC" width="" height="" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </a> </div> <div id="m3214" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r2310" class="row "> <div class="container container-fluid"><div id="c8803" class="col col-sm-12"><nav id="m5000" class="module nav smallModule" data-settings="vertical=false,direction=right,push=true,verticalNav-lg=false,activeParent=false,verticalNav-sm=false,verticalNav-md=true" tabindex="-1"> <ul class="navContainer"><li class=" active"> <a href="/" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Home</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/tree-removals-tree-surgery-woking" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Tree Removal</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/pruning-services" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Pruning Services</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/hedge-services-hedge-trimming-woking" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Hedge Services</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/deadwood-removal-garden-clearance-woking" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Deadwood Removal</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/stump-grinding-stump-removal-woking" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Stump Grinding</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/planting-tree-planting-woking" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Planting</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/gallery-woking" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Gallery</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/about-us-woking" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">About Us</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/contact-us-woking" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Contact Us</a> </li><li class=" hidden-lg hidden-md hidden-sm"> <a href="/thank-you" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Thank You</a> </li><li class=" hidden-lg hidden-md hidden-sm"> <a href="/privacy-policy" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Privacy Policy</a> </li></ul> </nav></div> </div> </div> </header><div id="r5002" role="main" class="row designRow"> <div class="container container-fluid"><div class="col col-sm-12"><div class="rowGroup" data-req="rowgroup" data-rowgroupsettings="auto=true" data-arrow-before="Before" data-arrow-after="After"> <div id="r1919" class="row inRowgroupView"> <div class="container container-fixed"><div class="col col-sm-12 flexCol"><div id="m2984" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r4047" class="row outOfRowgroupView hiddenBG"> <div class="container container-fixed"><div class="col col-sm-12 flexCol"><div id="m3908" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r1349" class="row outOfRowgroupView hiddenBG"> <div class="container container-fixed"><div class="col col-sm-12 flexCol"><div id="m4007" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r2040" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed colsStack"><div id="c9331" class="col col-md-3 col-lg-3 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m3342" class="module text smallModule"><h2 class="lightsubtitle">Tree Removals</h2></div> <div id="m1166" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">Arrange safe and effective removals for dead, dangerous, diseased, or unwanted trees.</p></div> </div> <div id="m1790" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <a id="m3809" class="module button" href="/tree-removals-tree-surgery-woking"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Read More</span> </a></div> </div> <div id="c1994" class="col col-sm-3 col-md-1 hidden-sm"></div> <div id="c4544" class="col col-md-3 col-lg-2 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m1316" class="module text"><h2 class="lightsubtitle">Pruning Services</h2></div> <div id="m1009" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">Maintain the look of your trees with effective crown reduction, pollarding, lifting, and thinning.</p></div> </div> <div id="m1267" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <a id="m3055" class="module button" href="/pruning-services"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Read More</span> </a></div> </div> <div id="c1042" class="col col-sm-2 col-md-1 hidden-sm hidden-md"></div> <div id="c2834" class="col col-md-2 col-lg-1 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m1753" class="module text"><h2 class="lightsubtitle">Hedge Services</h2></div> <div id="m4411" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">We can reduce the height of your hedge, cut the sides or the face to create a narrower and shorter hedge.</p></div> </div> <div id="m2317" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <a id="m3984" class="module button" href="/hedge-services-hedge-trimming-woking"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Read More</span> </a></div> </div> <div id="c4691" class="col col-sm-1 col-md-1 Col hidden-sm hidden-lg"></div> <div id="c4540" class="col col-md-3 col-lg-2 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m2397" class="module text"><h2 class="lightsubtitle">Deadwood Removal</h2></div> <div id="m2621" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">Clear dead branches and fallen deadwood from your garden for safety and aesthetic reasons.</p></div> </div> <div id="m3325" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <a id="m3097" class="module button" href="/deadwood-removal-garden-clearance-woking"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Read More</span> </a></div> </div> <div id="c4221" class="col col-sm-2 col-md-1 hidden-sm hidden-md"></div> <div id="c3207" class="col col-md-3 col-lg-1 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m4199" class="module text"><h2 class="lightsubtitle">Stump Grinding</h2></div> <div id="m3625" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">Reduce or remove problem stumps on your property with our efficient tree surgery solutions.</p></div> </div> <div id="m3665" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <a id="m4685" class="module button" href="/stump-grinding-stump-removal-woking"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Read More</span> </a></div> </div> <div id="c3967" class="col col-sm-1 col-md-1 hidden-sm"></div> <div id="c1345" class="col col-md-3 col-lg-3 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m2428" class="module text"><h2 class="lightsubtitle">Tree Planting</h2></div> <div id="m2393" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">Enhance your garden’s appeal with new trees and hedges planted by our professional team.</p></div> </div> <div id="m1672" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <a id="m3010" class="module button" href="/planting-tree-planting-woking"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Read More</span> </a></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r3819" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed colsStack"><div id="c4745" class="col col-sm-12 col-md-6 flexCol"><div id="m2385" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <div class="imageModuleWrap" id="w_m2046"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="Furness Tree Care Ltd" data-author="" width="" height="" fetchpriority="high"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/YHS6jhcH/IMG_0175_edited.webp" data-lazyload-id="m2046" data-lazyload-class="module image hidden-md hidden-lg" data-lazyload-alt="Furness Tree Care Ltd" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=,hovertransition="> <img id="m2046" class="module image hidden-md hidden-lg" src="/uploads/YHS6jhcH/IMG_0175_edited.webp" alt="Furness Tree Care Ltd" width="" height="" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </div><div id="m4216" class="module text"><h2 class="headline">About Us</h2></div> <div id="m1945" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">As fully qualified and insured tree surgeons, the team at Furness Tree Care Ltd are ideally placed to deliver tree services throughout Woking, Surrey, and the surrounding areas. Backed by more than 10 years of tree surgery experience, we cover all aspects of felling, grinding, pruning, removal, and clearance. We strive to work to the British Standard 3998 recommendation for tree works. Get in touch today with any enquiries.</p></div> </div> <div id="m4830" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> <div id="c1890" class="col col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-sm Col Col"></div> </div> </div> <div id="r2647" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed"><div id="c5498" class="col col-lg-7 col-md-8 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div id="m4978" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m4905" class="module text"><h1 class="lightpreamble">efficient and competent tree surgeons</h1></div> <div id="m4377" class="module text"><p class="lightbodytext" style="text-align: left;">Our experienced tree surgeons provide a wide array of tree services to suit your needs.</p></div> </div> <div id="m4877" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> <div id="c3120" class="col col-lg-5 col-md-4 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div id="m4408" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <a id="m3617" class="module button2" href="/contact-us-woking"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <i class="buttonIcon fa fa-tree fa-solid "></i> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight"> Get in Touch</span> </a> </div> <div id="m4023" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <footer><div id="r1986" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed"><div class="col col-md-3 col-lg-3 col-sm-12 hidden-md hidden-sm"> <div class="imageModuleWrap" id="w_m3638"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="Furness Tree Care Ltd - Logo" data-author="" width="202" height="202" fetchpriority="high"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/1molhXVL/Logo_377__msi___jpg.jpg" data-lazyload-id="m3638" data-lazyload-class="module image" data-lazyload-alt="Furness Tree Care Ltd - Logo" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=,hovertransition="> <img id="m3638" class="module image" src="/uploads/1molhXVL/Logo_377__msi___jpg.jpg" alt="Furness Tree Care Ltd - Logo" width="202" height="202" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </div></div> <div id="c4861" class="col col-lg-3 col-sm-12 col-md-4"><div id="m2416" class="module text"><p class="custom1">Contact Details</p></div> <div id="m1843" class="module text"><p class="footertext">Pankhurst Farm, Bagshot Rd,</p><p class="footertext">West End, Woking,</p><p class="footertext">Surrey, GU24 9QR</p></div> <div id="m1440" class="module text"><p class="footertext">Phone: <a data-global="phone"  href="tel:07472377454" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="phone_link"><span class="monoglobalWrap">07472 377454</span></a></p></div> <div id="m3967" class="module text"><p class="footertext">Email: <a href="mailto:furnesstc25@outlook.com" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="email_link"><span class="monoglobalWrap">furnesstc25@outlook.com</span></a></p></div> <ul id="m3564" class="module socialmedia"> <li class=" "> <a class="" href="https://www.instagram.com/furnesstreecare/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Instagram | Furness Tree Care Ltd" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="social_link"> <span class="fa fa-instagram"></span> </a> </li> </ul></div> <div id="c2125" class="col col-lg-3 col-sm-12 col-md-4"><div id="m1990" class="module text"><p class="custom1">Business Hours</p></div> <div class="module openinghours2" id="m3165"> <p class="day clear footertext"> <span class="dayLabel">Monday</span> <span class="ranges"> <span>08:00 - 20:00</span> </span> </p> <p class="day clear footertext"> <span class="dayLabel">Tuesday</span> <span class="ranges"> <span>08:00 - 20:00</span> </span> </p> <p class="day clear footertext"> <span class="dayLabel">Wednesday</span> <span class="ranges"> <span>08:00 - 20:00</span> </span> </p> <p class="day clear footertext"> <span class="dayLabel">Thursday</span> <span class="ranges"> <span>08:00 - 20:00</span> </span> </p> <p class="day clear footertext"> <span class="dayLabel">Friday</span> <span class="ranges"> <span>08:00 - 20:00</span> </span> </p> <p class="day clear footertext"> <span class="dayLabel">Saturday</span> <span class="ranges"> <span>08:00 - 20:00</span> </span> </p> <p class="subtitle specialDayTitle"></p> </div> </div> <div id="c2445" class="col col-lg-3 col-sm-12 col-md-4"><div id="m1863" class="module text"><p class="custom1">Other Information</p></div> <div id="m3475" class="module text"><p class="footertext">Proudly Serving Customers within 10 Miles of Woking, Surrey</p></div> <div id="m1201" class="module text"><p class="footertext"><a href="/gallery-woking" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">View Our Gallery</a></p></div> <div id="m3514" class="module text"><p class="footertext"><a href="/privacy-policy" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Privacy Policy</a></p></div> </div> </div> </div> </footer> <div class="row brandfooter"> <div class="container container-fixed"> <div class="col col-sm-12" style="text-align: center"> &copy; 2026. Thomson Directories Ltd. The content of this website is owned by us and our licensors; copying of any content (including images) without our consent is in breach of our <a href="https://www.thomsonlocal.com/onlinemediaterms" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" style="font-weight:bold" data-track-event=